    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_1_textmap_13",
    "content": "大家还在继续喝茶聊天，\n<color=#ca8f50>{me}</color>要是觉得累了，\n可以<color=#97c344>回帐篷休息</color>咯！",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_2_textmap_14",
    "content": "继续聊天吧！",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_2_textmap_15",
    "content": "我先去休息了",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_3_textmap_16",
    "content": null,
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_3_textmap_17",
    "content": "那请按自己的喜好\n慢慢享受！",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_3_textmap_18",
    "content": null,
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_3_textmap_19",
    "content": "想要休息时，\n请在回帐篷前打声招呼吧，\n稍后有东西要给你。",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_4_textmap_20",
    "content": null,
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_4_textmap_21",
    "content": "好咯！\n稍等……\n这个交给你。",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_22",
    "content": null,
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_23",
    "content": "这个是露营用的床，\n请<color=#38b6c5>在帐篷里</color>，\n从<color=#38b6c5>背包中</color>鼠标左键选择<color=#38b6c5>使用</color>。",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_24",
    "content": null,
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_25",
    "content": "还有，在帐篷内的箱子里\n放着从络米商联选配的生活用品，\n请打开后放心使用。",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_26",
    "content": null,
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_27",
    "content": "鼠标左键点击<color=#38b6c5>打开箱子</color>，\n想要使用的话，鼠标左键点击物品就可以，\n想躺到床上休息，在床边<color=#38b6c5>按【交互键】</color>就可以。",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_28",
    "content": null,
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_29",
    "content": "可以在床上小憩一下，\n到了下午，\n我们要开始正式的生活建设。",
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_30",
    "content": null,
    "info": "_"
  },
  {
    "textid": "Performance_201301_5_textmap_31",
    "content": "那就，晚点见！",
    "info": "_"
  }
]